  "detailed_description": "Talesworth Adventure is a challenging, logic-based puzzle game that was originally launched on Kongregate. Use loot bags, one-way gates, and various other tools, to safely guide Questy through a maze of peril. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179100/extras/585c7604134c894cf25349ee065e794c.poster.avif?t=1696811050\" width=618 height=387 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2179100/extras/585c7604134c894cf25349ee065e794c.webm?t=1696811050\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span><br><br><strong>Features</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Challenge yourself to go for gold on 33 mind-boggling maps<br></li><li> Follow Questy on his journey to find the missing artifacts and defeat Boneyard. It's up to you to save Talesworth Kingdom!<br></li><li> Lots of achievements to keep you busy<br></li><li> Join the Discord to meet a fun and active community</li></ul>",
